---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <section class="bg-slate-950 py-16 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-white/70">FAQ</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-black tracking-tight">Answers for builders and stakeholders</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base text-white/70">
        Have questions about curated Ansiversa apps, integrations, or support? Browse the most common topics our teams discuss during onboarding.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mt-10 divide-y rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-soft">
        <details class="group p-6" open>
          <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between text-left">
            <span class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">Can I use Ansiversa without Flowbite or heavy UI kits?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180" aria-hidden="true">⌄</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
            Yes. The entire system is built with Tailwind CSS + Alpine.js, aligned with our global tokens. You can adopt any component selectively.
          </p>
        </details>
        <details class="group p-6">
          <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between text-left">
            <span class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">Does it integrate with Astro DB and serverless auth?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180" aria-hidden="true">⌄</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
            Absolutely. We ship ready-to-use schemas, server actions, and helper utilities so your sessions, tokens, and verification flows are secure.
          </p>
        </details>
        <details class="group p-6">
          <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between text-left">
            <span class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">How opinionated is the Stripe setup?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180" aria-hidden="true">⌄</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
            Stripe integration is modular. Swap plans or add usage-based billing with minimal tweaks while keeping webhook security intact.
          </p>
        </details>
        <details class="group p-6">
          <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between text-left">
            <span class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">What support do I get on Pro versus Enterprise?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180" aria-hidden="true">⌄</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
            Pro includes priority async support and roadmap input. Enterprise customers get a dedicated engineer, migration help, and compliance reviews.
          </p>
        </details>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-8 text-center text-sm text-slate-500">
        Need something else? Email us at <a class="font-medium text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500" href="mailto:hello@ansiversa.com">hello@ansiversa.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
